1 Installation
**************

Nael's LSP-based features (via Eglot or lsp-mode), require Lean version
4 to be installed (https://lean-lang.org/install/manual/).  If you want
to use lsp-mode, you might need to install lsp-mode before ‘nael-lsp’.

